  - Additional refreshes triggered by fetchNews() integration (every 5 seconds)
  - Batches observed at: 00:15:56, 00:16:01, 00:16:06, 00:16:11, 00:16:16

### Assertion 4: Verify green/red coloring matches positive/negative change
PASS — Color coding verified via computed styles
